Privacy Policy for Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute Contact Directory Mobile App

Effective Date: 02-10-2024

Introduction

Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting the privacy and security of users of our mobile app. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our organization mobile app, which provides access to employee information and contact details. By using the app, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect The mobile app provides access to employee profiles and contact information within the organization. We do not collect, store, or process any personal data through the app, as it only serves as a directory for internal communication purposes. The information accessible through the app includes:

Employee names
Job titles
Departmental affiliations
Contact information techunonet2@gmail.com, 01918757070
This information is strictly limited to internal organizational use and is accessible only to authorized personnel.

2. How We Use Information The app is designed to enhance internal communication within the Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute. The information provided through the app is solely used for the following purposes:

Enabling employees to find contact information of their colleagues for communication and collaboration.
Facilitating team connectivity and efficient internal operations.
No personal or sensitive data is collected, shared, or used outside of these purposes.

3. Information Sharing and Disclosure The information within the app is only accessible to authorized employees of Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute. We do not share or disclose any employee data to third parties unless required by law or with the explicit consent of the individual.

4. Data Security We take the security of our employees' information seriously and have implemented reasonable administrative, technical, and physical measures to protect it from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no security system is completely infallible, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of the data.

5. Your Privacy Rights Since the app does not collect or store personal data, there are no specific privacy rights to exercise in relation to the app. However, if you have any concerns regarding the information displayed within the app or wish to correct any inaccurate data, please contact us.

6. Changes to this Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted within the app, and the "Effective Date" at the top will be updated accordingly.

7. Contact Us If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the use of our mobile app, please contact us at:

Bangladesh Agricultural Research Institute
Gazipur 1704
Phone: 01918757070
Email: techunonet2@gmail.com

By using the app, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
